quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  27,23,"“Ndawana mukadzi achivatonga, uye akapihwa zvinhu zvose zvinokwanisa kuitwa nemutongi (mambo) wose panyika, uye ane chigaro cheumambo chihombe.”"
  27,24,"“Ndamuwana iye nevanhu vake vachinamata zuva pachinhambwe chaAllah, uye Satani avanatsira mabasa avo kwavari, uye avatendeutsa kubva kunzira yakatwasuka, saka havana kutungamirwa.”"
  27,25,"“Havapfugamiri Allah avo vanoburitsa pachena izvo zvakavandika mumatenga uye nepanyika, uye vanoziva izvo zvamunovanza uye izvo zvamunoburitsa pachena.”"
  27,26,"“Allah, Laa ilaaha illaa Huwa (Hakuna vamwe mwari vane kodzero yekunamatwa kunze kwavo), Tenzi vechigaro chikuru!”"
  27,27,"Sulaimaan (Soromoni)) akati: “Tichaona kuti uri kutaura chokwadi here kana kuti uri weavo vanonyepa.”"
  27,28,"“Enda netsamba yangu iyi, uye wovapa, uye wobva kwavari, uye woona kuti vanoti kudini.”"
  27,29,"Mambokadzi weSaba’ (Sheba)) akati: “Imi makurukota! Zvirokwazvo, ndaunzirwa tsamba inoremekedzeka.”"
  27,30,"“Zvirokwazvo, yabva kuna Sulaimaan (Soromoni), uye zvirokwazvo iri kuti: ‘Muzita raAllah, vane nyasha, vane tsitsi.’"
  27,31,"‘Musava munozvitutumadza kwandiri, asi huyai kwandiri muchizvipira kuna Allah (semaMuslim).’”"
  27,32,"Akati: “Imi makurukota! Ndipei pfungwa dzenyu panyaya yangu iyi. Handitongi nyaya kusvikira imi mavapo pandiri (mandipa pfungwa dzenyu).”"
  27,33,"Vakati: “Tine simba rakawanda, uye tinogona hondo zvakanyanya, asi zviri kwamuri kupa mutongo. Saka fungai ndeupi mutongo wamuchapa.”"
  27,34,"Akati: “Zvirokwazvo madzimambo, kana vapinda muguta (munyika) vanoiparadza, uye voita vanhu vanoremekedzwa pakati pavo vanhu vepasi pasi. Saizvozvo vanoita.”"
  27,35,"“Asi zvirokwazvo, ndichavatumira chipo, uye ndoona kuti vatumwa vanodzoka nei.”"